# Testing Standards

## 測試框架

| 層次 | 工具 |
|---|---|
| Unit (TS) | **Vitest** |
| Component | **Vitest + React Testing Library** |
| E2E | **Playwright** |
| Solidity | **Foundry forge** |
| API contract | **Pactum** 或自製 |
| Visual regression | **Chromatic** 或 Playwright screenshot |

---

## 測試金字塔

```
        E2E
       /    \
  Integration
  /          \
Unit (大量)
```

- 70% Unit
- 20% Integration
- 10% E2E

---

## 覆蓋率目標

| Package / App | 目標 |
|---|---|
| `apps/api` (domain layer) | > 90% |
| `apps/api` (application layer) | > 85% |
| `apps/api` (infrastructure) | > 70% |
| `apps/web` / `apps/console` | > 60% |
| `packages/contracts` | **100% 函式覆蓋率** |
| `packages/ui` | 透過 stories 覆蓋 |
| `packages/shared` | > 90% |

CI 強制：覆蓋率下降 > 5% PR 不可 merge。

